dc_description_s: Map shows tram, trolley, bus and petrol bus routes, railways, street numbers, public telephones, quarries, and post boxes. Includes index to map coverage. Crown copyright reserved. "For general gazetteer of banks, churches, government offices, hospitals, and many other features shown on these maps see pages 38-44." Drawn by the Mapping Branch of the Lands and Surveys Department from aerial photostaken in connection with the Aerial Survey of Tasmania--page 53. Map Collection does not have the companion gazetteer.
dc_creator_sm: Tasmania. Lands and Surveys Department. Mapping Branch
